tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE WebsiteTraffic (
    ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    UserIP VARCHAR(255),
    PageVisited VARCHAR(255),
    InteractionType VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE shopping_experience (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url VARCHAR(255),
    visitor_ip VARCHAR(50),
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE shopping_cart (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    added_to_cart_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    registration_date TIMESTAMP,
    last_login TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE page_views (
    view_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
    page_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES website_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE purchase_history (
    purchase_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    purchase_date DATE NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES website_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE cart_items (
    cart_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    quantity INTEGER NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES website_users(user_id)
);
